<div class="col about-page">
  <span class="anchor" id="about-work-section"></span>
  <div class="row bg-yellow about-page-section pt-5 pb-5" id="about-work">
    <div class="col">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center">
          <h1 class="main-heading pb-4 pt-5">Work</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center text-center text-md-left">
              <p>Having worked in higher education for a number of years, I have recently begun my career as a Junior Full Stack Web Developer (see <a href="#about-study-section">Study</a>) and will be completing a Web Developer internship in February 2018. You can see more of my work history on my <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/drbiancapower/">LinkedIn profile</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
