    <div class="col">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center">
          <h1 class="main-heading pb-4">Study</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center text-center text-md-left">
              <p>I am currently training to be a junior full stack web developer, completing a Diploma of Information Technology through <a href="https://coderacademy.edu.au/fast-track">Coder Academy's Fast Track program</a>. In a former life, my education included a Bachelor of Education (Primary)(Hons) and a PhD in Education. Yes, I'm highly educated in education.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <span class="anchor" id="about-life-section"></span>
  <div class="row bg-yellow about-page-section pt-5 pb-5" id="about-life">
    <div class="col">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center">
          <h1 class="main-heading pb-4">Life</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-center pb-4 pt-4 order-md-2">
          <%= image_tag "me_cubing_shirt.jpg", class:"img-fluid profile-photo rounded" %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-center text-md-left about-blurb d-flex justify-content-center align-items-md-center pt-4 order-md-1">
          <p>I live in Bondi, Australia with my amazing partner of 6 years. In my spare time I enjoy reading fantasy fiction and speedsolving Rubik's cubes and other twisty puzzles.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
